*`GIT_TRACE_SETUP`* shows information about what Git is discovering about the repository and environment it's interacting with.
//////////////////////////
*`GIT_TRACE_SETUP`* はGitがリポジトリや環境を操作する際に何を見ているかを表示します。

[source,console]
